title: Ep 123 - Thanksgiving Eve
description:
The boys got back to shooting the shit and letting it rip for this one. They talked all things Thanksgiving and cut loose about life a little. They even busted at a Thanksgiving-themed Maraldo’s Mad Lib.

There’s a bonus interview with actor/comedian Kevin Nealon at the end of this episode. Kevin chats a bit about his new YouTube show “Hiking with Kevin”. You can watch it now at

https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC0BfPXleDan8dMbel6-C89Q
